import React from "react"; function StampPreview(props) { const { jobName, jobCode, preparedFor, preparedBy, date, isRevision, jobPhase, gradientStyle, dateFormat, revisionNumber, boxFolder, boxFolderNumber, } = props; return (

Stamp Preview

Job Name: {jobName}

Job Code: {jobCode}

Prepared For: {preparedFor}

Prepared By: {preparedBy}

Date: {date.toLocaleDateString()}

Is Revision: {isRevision ? "Yes" : "No"}

Job Phase: {jobPhase}

Gradient Style: {gradientStyle}

Date Format: {dateFormat}

Revision Number: {revisionNumber}

Box Folder: {boxFolder}

Box Folder Number: {boxFolderNumber}

); } export default StampPreview;
